staticBinding.value: SELECT t.TSHIRTSIZE,t.CPU,t.RAM FROM SERVERSIZE sz INNER JOIN SERVER s ON sz.SERVERID=s.SERVERID INNER JOIN TSHIRTSIZES t ON t.TSHIRTSIZE = sz.TSHIRTSIZE WHERE s.CSASVCUUID = '${CSA_CONTEXT_ID}' and VALIDTO is null
SELECT ALLOCCPU,ALLOCRAM FROM MOERESPOOL WHERE RESPOOLID = '${server.resourcepool}'
